178	## Key Design Patterns
179	
180	- Soft, nurturing UI with 16px card radius and pill-shaped buttons (24px radius)
181	- Lavender primary (#7C3AED) with Blush Rose secondary (#F9A8D4) accents
182	- Bottom navigation with 4 tabs and active state indicator pills
183	- SVG-based inline icons throughout
184	- Nunito font family with generous line-height for calm readability
185	- Gentle spring-based animations (200-300ms ease-out transitions)
186	
187	## Implementation Notes
188	
189	- All screens use the 4-tab bottom navigation shell
190	- Push routes hide the bottom navigation bar
191	- Full-sheet overlays cover the entire screen (used for breathing exercise animation)
192	- Bottom-sheet overlays slide up from the bottom edge for contextual forms
193	- FAB appears on push routes that support entry creation (cycle-tracking, weight-nutrition, health-log)
