[2026-05-19T02:35:44.033Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_t7qzfe5ej709_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Settings Screen Specification\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Screen Title\n4\t\n5\t**Title:** Settings\n6\t**Widget Name:** `SettingsScreen`\n7\t**Screen ID:** `settings`\n8\t\n9\t---\n10\t\n11\t## 2. Purpose\n12\t\n13\tThe Settings screen allows users to manage their personal profile, configure notification preferences, export app data, and view legal/version information. It is a structured preference screen organized into four themed sections: Profile, Notifications, Data, and About.\n14\t\n15\t---\n16\t\n17\t## 3. Route\n18\t\n19\t**Route:** `/settings`\n20\t**Navigation Type:** Push (from Profile tab or Settings icon in Home AppBar)\n21\t**Swipe-back:** Enabled (dismisses to previous screen)\n22\t\n23\t---\n24\t\n25\t## 4. Design Tokens\n26\t\n27\t### Colors (Light Theme)\n28\t\n29\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n30\t|---|---|---|\n31\t| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary actions, section headers, AppBar title |\n32\t| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n33\t| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n34\t| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text (titles, names) |\n35\t| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, descriptions |\n36\t| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | List item borders, toggles off state |\n37\t| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Clear data / destructive actions |\n38\t| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states (export complete) |\n39\t| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Card surfaces, bottom sheets |\n40\t\n41\t### Typography (Nunito)\n42\t\n43\t| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n44\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n45\t| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | Screen title |\n46\t| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Section headers |\n47\t| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | List item titles, field labels |\n48\t| `bodySmall` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Descriptions, secondary text |\n49\t| `caption` | 12sp | 400 | 16sp | Metadata, hints, version text |\n50\t\n51\t### Spacing (8pt Base)\n52\t\n53\t| Token | Value |\n54\t|---|---|\n55\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n56\t| `md` | 16dp |\n57\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n58\t\n59\t### Corner Radius\n60\t\n61\t| Token | Value |\n62\t|---|---|\n63\t| `card` | 16dp |\n64\t| `listItem` | 12dp |\n65\t\n66\t### Motion\n67\t\n68\t| Motion | Duration | Curve |\n69\t|---|---|---|\n70\t| Screen push transition | 300ms | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n71\t| List item stagger reveal | 50ms delay between items | `Curves.easeOut` |\n72\t| Toggle switch thumb | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` |\n73\t| Card tap feedback | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` (scale to 98%) |\n74\t| Export success toast | 300ms fade in/out | `Curves.easeOut` |\n75\t\n76\t---\n77\t\n78\t## 5. Layout Rules\n79\t\n80\t### Scaffold Structure\n81\t\n82\t```\n83\tScaffold\n84\t├── AppBar\n85\t│   ├── Title: \"Settings\" (titleLarge, deepGraphite)\n86\t│   ├── Back button (leading, 48dp touch target)\n87\t│   └── No trailing icons\n88\t├── BottomNavigationBar: Hidden\n89\t├── FAB: None\n90\t└── Body: ListView (sections separated by 24dp spacing)\n91\t```\n92\t\n93\t### AppBar Behavior\n94\t- Background: lavenderTint (#F5F3FF), transparent feel\n95\t- Title: centered or left-aligned, SemiBold 20sp, deepGraphite\n96\t- Back button: icon button with lavenderBloom color on tap\n97\t- No actions/trailing widgets\n98\t\n99\t### Body Layout\n100\t- Vertical `ListView` with `SliverAppBar` disabled (standard AppBar only)\n101\t- Cards are wrapped in `Padding` with 16dp horizontal margin\n102\t- 24dp vertical spacing between sections\n103\t- 12dp vertical spacing between items within a section\n104\t\n105\t### Bottom Navigation Bar\n106\t- Hidden on this screen (navType: push)\n107\t\n108\t---\n109\t\n110\t## 6. Sections\n111\t\n112\t### Section 1: Profile\n113\t\n114\t**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n115\t\n116\t**Content:**\n117\t- **Name field** — `TextFormField` or tappable row that opens inline edit or bottom sheet. Label: \"Name\", value from `UserPreferences.name`.\n118\t- **Due date row** — Tappable list tile showing due date. Label: \"Due Date\", value from `PregnancyProfile.dueDate` (also stored in `UserPreferences.dueDate`). Tapping triggers `showDatePicker` bottom sheet.\n119\t\n120\t**Data Requirements:**\n121\t- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `name` field\n122\t- `PregnancyProfileProvider` — `dueDate` field\n123\t\n124\t**Interactive Elements:**\n125\t- Name tap → inline edit or bottom sheet with `TextEditingController`\n126\t- Due date tap → `showDatePicker` bottom sheet, saves to both providers\n127\t\n128\t---\n129\t\n130\t### Section 2: Notifications\n131\t\n132\t**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n133\t\n134\t**Content:**\n135\tA `Column` of `SwitchListTile` widgets, one per notification category:\n136\t1. **Daily Reminders** — `UserPreferences.notifications.dailyReminders`\n137\t2. **Symptom Alerts** — `UserPreferences.notifications.symptomAlerts`\n138\t3. **Appointment Reminders** — `UserPreferences.notifications.appointmentReminders`\n139\t4. **Weekly Digest** — `UserPreferences.notifications.weeklyDigest`\n140\t\n141\tEach switch:\n142\t- Title: notification category name (titleMedium, deepGraphite)\n143\t- Subtitle: brief description (bodySmall, stoneGrey)\n144\t- Active track color: lavenderBloom; inactive track: mistyBorder\n145\t\n146\t**Data Requirements:**\n147\t- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `notificationsEnabled`, individual category flags\n148\t\n149\t**Interactive Elements:**\n150\t- Toggle switch → `UserPreferencesProvider.updateNotification(category, enabled)`\n151\t- 200ms thumb slide animation\n152\t\n153\t---\n154\t\n155\t### Section 3: Data\n156\t\n157\t**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n158\t\n159\t**Content:**\n160\tTwo action rows:\n161\t1. **Export Data** — `InkWell` or `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → generates JSON/CSV file of all user data, triggers system share sheet.\n162\t2. **Clear All Data** — `ListTile` with icon and label in softCoral color. Tap → `AlertDialog` confirmation (\"Are you sure? This action cannot be undone.\"), then calls `UserPreferencesProvider.clearAll()`.\n163\t\n164\t**Data Requirements:**\n165\t- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `clearAll()` method\n166\t- Export uses all provider data (pregnancy profile, mood entries, weight entries, health log)\n167\t\n168\t**Interactive Elements:**\n169\t- Export tap → generate file → `Share.share()` system share sheet\n170\t- Clear tap → `showDialog()` with `AlertDialog` → confirmation calls `clearAll()` and shows success snackbar\n171\t\n172\t---\n173\t\n174\t### Section 4: About\n175\t\n176\t**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n177\t\n178\t**Content:**\n179\tThree rows:\n180\t1. **App Version** — Static text row: \"Version\" label + version string from `pubspec.yaml` (e.g., \"1.0.0\"). Non-interactive.\n181\t2. **Privacy Policy** — `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → opens external URL (e.g., `https://example.com/privacy`).\n182\t3. **Terms of Service** — `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → opens external URL (e.g., `https://example.com/terms`).\n183\t\n184\t**Interactive Elements:**\n185\t- Privacy Policy tap → `url_launcher.launchUrl()` with privacy policy URL\n186\t- Terms of Service tap → `url_launcher.launchUrl()` with terms URL\n187\t\n188\t---\n189\t\n190\t## 7. Data\n191\t\n192\t### Entities\n193\t\n194\t| Entity | Provider | Key Fields |\n195\t|---|---|---|\n196\t| `UserPreferences` | `UserPreferencesProvider` | `name`, `notificationsEnabled`, `dueDate` |\n197\t| `PregnancyProfile` | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | `dueDate`, `currentWeek` |\n198\t\n199\t### Provider Scope\n200\t\n201\t- `UserPreferencesProvider` — manages name, notification preferences, due date (shared with PregnancyProfile)\n202\t- `PregnancyProfileProvider` — manages due date, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek\n203\t\n204\t### Export File Format\n205\t\n206\tJSON format containing:\n207\t```json\n208\t{\n209\t  \"exportDate\": \"ISO8601 timestamp\",\n210\t  \"user\": { \"name\": \"...\", \"dueDate\": \"...\" },\n211\t  \"pregnancyProfile\": { ... },\n212\t  \"moodEntries\": [ ... ],\n213\t  \"weightEntries\": [ ... ],\n214\t  \"symptomEntries\": [ ... ],\n215\t  \"cycleEntries\": [ ... ]\n216\t}\n217\t```\n218\t\n219\t---\n220\t\n221\t## 8. Motion\n222\t\n223\t### Screen Transition\n224\t- **Duration:** 300ms\n225\t- **Curve:** `Curves.easeInOut`\n226\t- **Type:** Slide + fade (standard push transition)\n227\t\n228\t### List Item Reveal\n229\t- **Stagger:** 50ms between each item (from top to bottom)\n230\t- **Type:** Fade + slight slide up\n231\t- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`\n232\t\n233\t### Toggle Switch\n234\t- **Duration:** 200ms\n235\t- **Type:** Thumb slide, track color transition\n236\t\n237\t### Card Tap Feedback\n238\t- **Duration:** 200ms\n239\t- **Type:** Scale to 98%, then return to 100%\n240\t- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`\n241\t\n242\t### Export Success\n243\t- **Duration:** 300ms\n244\t- **Type:** SnackBar fade in from bottom, auto-dismiss after 3s\n245\t\n246\t---\n247\t\n248\t## 9. Accessibility\n249\t\n250\t### Semantic Labels\n251\t- **Name field:** \"User name, [current name], double tap to edit\"\n252\t- **Due date:** \"Due date, [formatted date], double tap to change\"\n253\t- **Notification toggles:** \"[Category name], notifications [enabled/disabled], double tap to toggle\"\n254\t- **Export Data:** \"Export data, double tap to save and share your data\"\n255\t- **Clear All Data:** \"Clear all data, double tap to delete all app data. This action cannot be undone.\"\n256\t- **Privacy Policy:** \"Privacy policy, opens in browser\"\n257\t- **Terms of Service:** \"Terms of service, opens in browser\"\n258\t\n259\t### Touch Targets\n260\t- All interactive list items: minimum 56dp height\n261\t- All switches: 48dp minimum touch target\n262\t- All buttons: 48dp minimum height\n263\t\n264\t### Focus Order\n265\t1. Name field\n266\t2. Due date row\n267\t3. Daily Reminders toggle\n268\t4. Symptom Alerts toggle\n269\t5. Appointment Reminders toggle\n270\t6. Weekly Digest toggle\n271\t7. Export Data\n272\t8. Clear All Data\n273\t9. Privacy Policy\n274\t10. Terms of Service\n275\t\n276\t### Color Contrast\n277\t- Primary text (deepGraphite #1F2937) on morningMist (#FAFAFA): 12.8:1 ratio (AA compliant)\n278\t- Secondary text (stoneGrey #6B7280) on morningMist: 4.6:1 ratio (AA compliant)\n279\t- All text meets WCAG 2.1 AA contrast requirements\n280\t\n281\t---\n282\t\n283\t## 10. Anti-Patterns\n284\t\n285\t### Do NOT\n286\t- Use platform default colors — all colors from design token palette\n287\t- Show bottom navigation bar on this screen (hidden by navType: push)\n288\t- Use `AlertDialog` for anything other than destructive confirmation (clear data)\n289\t- Place critical actions (clear data) outside thumb zone (bottom two-thirds of screen)\n290\t- Use Inter or Roboto — Nunito only\n291\t- Use sharp corners — all cards 16dp radius, list items 12dp radius\n292\t- Use generic \"OK\" button labels — use action-specific labels (\"Delete\", \"Cancel\", \"Export\")\n293\t- Show FAB on this screen\n294\t- Use hardcoded strings — extract to localization keys"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3ddfff14-cec4-47ac-93d0-cd853b5c8ae4","uuid":"133ac7bd-e9f8-4c98-9dd0-0a7c8cb944a9","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:35:44.032Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/settings/SPEC.md","content":"# Settings Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n\n**Title:** Settings\n**Widget Name:** `SettingsScreen`\n**Screen ID:** `settings`\n\n---\n\n## 2. Purpose\n\nThe Settings screen allows users to manage their personal profile, configure notification preferences, export app data, and view legal/version information. It is a structured preference screen organized into four themed sections: Profile, Notifications, Data, and About.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Route\n\n**Route:** `/settings`\n**Navigation Type:** Push (from Profile tab or Settings icon in Home AppBar)\n**Swipe-back:** Enabled (dismisses to previous screen)\n\n---\n\n## 4. Design Tokens\n\n### Colors (Light Theme)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary actions, section headers, AppBar title |\n| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text (titles, names) |\n| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, descriptions |\n| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | List item borders, toggles off state |\n| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Clear data / destructive actions |\n| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states (export complete) |\n| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Card surfaces, bottom sheets |\n\n### Typography (Nunito)\n\n| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | Screen title |\n| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Section headers |\n| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | List item titles, field labels |\n| `bodySmall` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Descriptions, secondary text |\n| `caption` | 12sp | 400 | 16sp | Metadata, hints, version text |\n\n### Spacing (8pt Base)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n\n### Corner Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `card` | 16dp |\n| `listItem` | 12dp |\n\n### Motion\n\n| Motion | Duration | Curve |\n|---|---|---|\n| Screen push transition | 300ms | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n| List item stagger reveal | 50ms delay between items | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| Toggle switch thumb | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| Card tap feedback | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` (scale to 98%) |\n| Export success toast | 300ms fade in/out | `Curves.easeOut` |\n\n---\n\n## 5. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n\n```\nScaffold\n├── AppBar\n│   ├── Title: \"Settings\" (titleLarge, deepGraphite)\n│   ├── Back button (leading, 48dp touch target)\n│   └── No trailing icons\n├── BottomNavigationBar: Hidden\n├── FAB: None\n└── Body: ListView (sections separated by 24dp spacing)\n```\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n- Background: lavenderTint (#F5F3FF), transparent feel\n- Title: centered or left-aligned, SemiBold 20sp, deepGraphite\n- Back button: icon button with lavenderBloom color on tap\n- No actions/trailing widgets\n\n### Body Layout\n- Vertical `ListView` with `SliverAppBar` disabled (standard AppBar only)\n- Cards are wrapped in `Padding` with 16dp horizontal margin\n- 24dp vertical spacing between sections\n- 12dp vertical spacing between items within a section\n\n### Bottom Navigation Bar\n- Hidden on this screen (navType: push)\n\n---\n\n## 6. Sections\n\n### Section 1: Profile\n\n**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n\n**Content:**\n- **Name field** — `TextFormField` or tappable row that opens inline edit or bottom sheet. Label: \"Name\", value from `UserPreferences.name`.\n- **Due date row** — Tappable list tile showing due date. Label: \"Due Date\", value from `PregnancyProfile.dueDate` (also stored in `UserPreferences.dueDate`). Tapping triggers `showDatePicker` bottom sheet.\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `name` field\n- `PregnancyProfileProvider` — `dueDate` field\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Name tap → inline edit or bottom sheet with `TextEditingController`\n- Due date tap → `showDatePicker` bottom sheet, saves to both providers\n\n---\n\n### Section 2: Notifications\n\n**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n\n**Content:**\nA `Column` of `SwitchListTile` widgets, one per notification category:\n1. **Daily Reminders** — `UserPreferences.notifications.dailyReminders`\n2. **Symptom Alerts** — `UserPreferences.notifications.symptomAlerts`\n3. **Appointment Reminders** — `UserPreferences.notifications.appointmentReminders`\n4. **Weekly Digest** — `UserPreferences.notifications.weeklyDigest`\n\nEach switch:\n- Title: notification category name (titleMedium, deepGraphite)\n- Subtitle: brief description (bodySmall, stoneGrey)\n- Active track color: lavenderBloom; inactive track: mistyBorder\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `notificationsEnabled`, individual category flags\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Toggle switch → `UserPreferencesProvider.updateNotification(category, enabled)`\n- 200ms thumb slide animation\n\n---\n\n### Section 3: Data\n\n**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n\n**Content:**\nTwo action rows:\n1. **Export Data** — `InkWell` or `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → generates JSON/CSV file of all user data, triggers system share sheet.\n2. **Clear All Data** — `ListTile` with icon and label in softCoral color. Tap → `AlertDialog` confirmation (\"Are you sure? This action cannot be undone.\"), then calls `UserPreferencesProvider.clearAll()`.\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `clearAll()` method\n- Export uses all provider data (pregnancy profile, mood entries, weight entries, health log)\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Export tap → generate file → `Share.share()` system share sheet\n- Clear tap → `showDialog()` with `AlertDialog` → confirmation calls `clearAll()` and shows success snackbar\n\n---\n\n### Section 4: About\n\n**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n\n**Content:**\nThree rows:\n1. **App Version** — Static text row: \"Version\" label + version string from `pubspec.yaml` (e.g., \"1.0.0\"). Non-interactive.\n2. **Privacy Policy** — `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → opens external URL (e.g., `https://example.com/privacy`).\n3. **Terms of Service** — `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → opens external URL (e.g., `https://example.com/terms`).\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Privacy Policy tap → `url_launcher.launchUrl()` with privacy policy URL\n- Terms of Service tap → `url_launcher.launchUrl()` with terms URL\n\n---\n\n## 7. Data\n\n### Entities\n\n| Entity | Provider | Key Fields |\n|---|---|---|\n| `UserPreferences` | `UserPreferencesProvider` | `name`, `notificationsEnabled`, `dueDate` |\n| `PregnancyProfile` | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | `dueDate`, `currentWeek` |\n\n### Provider Scope\n\n- `UserPreferencesProvider` — manages name, notification preferences, due date (shared with PregnancyProfile)\n- `PregnancyProfileProvider` — manages due date, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek\n\n### Export File Format\n\nJSON format containing:\n```json\n{\n  \"exportDate\": \"ISO8601 timestamp\",\n  \"user\": { \"name\": \"...\", \"dueDate\": \"...\" },\n  \"pregnancyProfile\": { ... },\n  \"moodEntries\": [ ... ],\n  \"weightEntries\": [ ... ],\n  \"symptomEntries\": [ ... ],\n  \"cycleEntries\": [ ... ]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 8. Motion\n\n### Screen Transition\n- **Duration:** 300ms\n- **Curve:** `Curves.easeInOut`\n- **Type:** Slide + fade (standard push transition)\n\n### List Item Reveal\n- **Stagger:** 50ms between each item (from top to bottom)\n- **Type:** Fade + slight slide up\n- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`\n\n### Toggle Switch\n- **Duration:** 200ms\n- **Type:** Thumb slide, track color transition\n\n### Card Tap Feedback\n- **Duration:** 200ms\n- **Type:** Scale to 98%, then return to 100%\n- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`\n\n### Export Success\n- **Duration:** 300ms\n- **Type:** SnackBar fade in from bottom, auto-dismiss after 3s\n\n---\n\n## 9. Accessibility\n\n### Semantic Labels\n- **Name field:** \"User name, [current name], double tap to edit\"\n- **Due date:** \"Due date, [formatted date], double tap to change\"\n- **Notification toggles:** \"[Category name], notifications [enabled/disabled], double tap to toggle\"\n- **Export Data:** \"Export data, double tap to save and share your data\"\n- **Clear All Data:** \"Clear all data, double tap to delete all app data. This action cannot be undone.\"\n- **Privacy Policy:** \"Privacy policy, opens in browser\"\n- **Terms of Service:** \"Terms of service, opens in browser\"\n\n### Touch Targets\n- All interactive list items: minimum 56dp height\n- All switches: 48dp minimum touch target\n- All buttons: 48dp minimum height\n\n### Focus Order\n1. Name field\n2. Due date row\n3. Daily Reminders toggle\n4. Symptom Alerts toggle\n5. Appointment Reminders toggle\n6. Weekly Digest toggle\n7. Export Data\n8. Clear All Data\n9. Privacy Policy\n10. Terms of Service\n\n### Color Contrast\n- Primary text (deepGraphite #1F2937) on morningMist (#FAFAFA): 12.8:1 ratio (AA compliant)\n- Secondary text (stoneGrey #6B7280) on morningMist: 4.6:1 ratio (AA compliant)\n- All text meets WCAG 2.1 AA contrast requirements\n\n---\n\n## 10. Anti-Patterns\n\n### Do NOT\n- Use platform default colors — all colors from design token palette\n- Show bottom navigation bar on this screen (hidden by navType: push)\n- Use `AlertDialog` for anything other than destructive confirmation (clear data)\n- Place critical actions (clear data) outside thumb zone (bottom two-thirds of screen)\n- Use Inter or Roboto — Nunito only\n- Use sharp corners — all cards 16dp radius, list items 12dp radius\n- Use generic \"OK\" button labels — use action-specific labels (\"Delete\", \"Cancel\", \"Export\")\n- Show FAB on this screen\n- Use hardcoded strings — extract to localization keys","numLines":294,"startLine":1,"totalLines":294}}}
[2026-05-19T02:35:44.035Z] [STREAM_EVENT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_t7qzfe5ej709_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Settings Screen Specification\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Screen Title\n4\t\n5\t**Title:** Settings\n6\t**Widget Name:** `SettingsScreen`\n7\t**Screen ID:** `settings`\n8\t\n9\t---\n10\t\n11\t## 2. Purpose\n12\t\n13\tThe Settings screen allows users to manage their personal profile, configure notification preferences, export app data, and view legal/version information. It is a structured preference screen organized into four themed sections: Profile, Notifications, Data, and About.\n14\t\n15\t---\n16\t\n17\t## 3. Route\n18\t\n19\t**Route:** `/settings`\n20\t**Navigation Type:** Push (from Profile tab or Settings icon in Home AppBar)\n21\t**Swipe-back:** Enabled (dismisses to previous screen)\n22\t\n23\t---\n24\t\n25\t## 4. Design Tokens\n26\t\n27\t### Colors (Light Theme)\n28\t\n29\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n30\t|---|---|---|\n31\t| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary actions, section headers, AppBar title |\n32\t| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n33\t| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n34\t| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text (titles, names) |\n35\t| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, descriptions |\n36\t| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | List item borders, toggles off state |\n37\t| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Clear data / destructive actions |\n38\t| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states (export complete) |\n39\t| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Card surfaces, bottom sheets |\n40\t\n41\t### Typography (Nunito)\n42\t\n43\t| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n44\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n45\t| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | Screen title |\n46\t| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Section headers |\n47\t| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | List item titles, field labels |\n48\t| `bodySmall` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Descriptions, secondary text |\n49\t| `caption` | 12sp | 400 | 16sp | Metadata, hints, version text |\n50\t\n51\t### Spacing (8pt Base)\n52\t\n53\t| Token | Value |\n54\t|---|---|\n55\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n56\t| `md` | 16dp |\n57\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n58\t\n59\t### Corner Radius\n60\t\n61\t| Token | Value |\n62\t|---|---|\n63\t| `card` | 16dp |\n64\t| `listItem` | 12dp |\n65\t\n66\t### Motion\n67\t\n68\t| Motion | Duration | Curve |\n69\t|---|---|---|\n70\t| Screen push transition | 300ms | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n71\t| List item stagger reveal | 50ms delay between items | `Curves.easeOut` |\n72\t| Toggle switch thumb | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` |\n73\t| Card tap feedback | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` (scale to 98%) |\n74\t| Export success toast | 300ms fade in/out | `Curves.easeOut` |\n75\t\n76\t---\n77\t\n78\t## 5. Layout Rules\n79\t\n80\t### Scaffold Structure\n81\t\n82\t```\n83\tScaffold\n84\t├── AppBar\n85\t│   ├── Title: \"Settings\" (titleLarge, deepGraphite)\n86\t│   ├── Back button (leading, 48dp touch target)\n87\t│   └── No trailing icons\n88\t├── BottomNavigationBar: Hidden\n89\t├── FAB: None\n90\t└── Body: ListView (sections separated by 24dp spacing)\n91\t```\n92\t\n93\t### AppBar Behavior\n94\t- Background: lavenderTint (#F5F3FF), transparent feel\n95\t- Title: centered or left-aligned, SemiBold 20sp, deepGraphite\n96\t- Back button: icon button with lavenderBloom color on tap\n97\t- No actions/trailing widgets\n98\t\n99\t### Body Layout\n100\t- Vertical `ListView` with `SliverAppBar` disabled (standard AppBar only)\n101\t- Cards are wrapped in `Padding` with 16dp horizontal margin\n102\t- 24dp vertical spacing between sections\n103\t- 12dp vertical spacing between items within a section\n104\t\n105\t### Bottom Navigation Bar\n106\t- Hidden on this screen (navType: push)\n107\t\n108\t---\n109\t\n110\t## 6. Sections\n111\t\n112\t### Section 1: Profile\n113\t\n114\t**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n115\t\n116\t**Content:**\n117\t- **Name field** — `TextFormField` or tappable row that opens inline edit or bottom sheet. Label: \"Name\", value from `UserPreferences.name`.\n118\t- **Due date row** — Tappable list tile showing due date. Label: \"Due Date\", value from `PregnancyProfile.dueDate` (also stored in `UserPreferences.dueDate`). Tapping triggers `showDatePicker` bottom sheet.\n119\t\n120\t**Data Requirements:**\n121\t- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `name` field\n122\t- `PregnancyProfileProvider` — `dueDate` field\n123\t\n124\t**Interactive Elements:**\n125\t- Name tap → inline edit or bottom sheet with `TextEditingController`\n126\t- Due date tap → `showDatePicker` bottom sheet, saves to both providers\n127\t\n128\t---\n129\t\n130\t### Section 2: Notifications\n131\t\n132\t**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n133\t\n134\t**Content:**\n135\tA `Column` of `SwitchListTile` widgets, one per notification category:\n136\t1. **Daily Reminders** — `UserPreferences.notifications.dailyReminders`\n137\t2. **Symptom Alerts** — `UserPreferences.notifications.symptomAlerts`\n138\t3. **Appointment Reminders** — `UserPreferences.notifications.appointmentReminders`\n139\t4. **Weekly Digest** — `UserPreferences.notifications.weeklyDigest`\n140\t\n141\tEach switch:\n142\t- Title: notification category name (titleMedium, deepGraphite)\n143\t- Subtitle: brief description (bodySmall, stoneGrey)\n144\t- Active track color: lavenderBloom; inactive track: mistyBorder\n145\t\n146\t**Data Requirements:**\n147\t- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `notificationsEnabled`, individual category flags\n148\t\n149\t**Interactive Elements:**\n150\t- Toggle switch → `UserPreferencesProvider.updateNotification(category, enabled)`\n151\t- 200ms thumb slide animation\n152\t\n153\t---\n154\t\n155\t### Section 3: Data\n156\t\n157\t**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n158\t\n159\t**Content:**\n160\tTwo action rows:\n161\t1. **Export Data** — `InkWell` or `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → generates JSON/CSV file of all user data, triggers system share sheet.\n162\t2. **Clear All Data** — `ListTile` with icon and label in softCoral color. Tap → `AlertDialog` confirmation (\"Are you sure? This action cannot be undone.\"), then calls `UserPreferencesProvider.clearAll()`.\n163\t\n164\t**Data Requirements:**\n165\t- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `clearAll()` method\n166\t- Export uses all provider data (pregnancy profile, mood entries, weight entries, health log)\n167\t\n168\t**Interactive Elements:**\n169\t- Export tap → generate file → `Share.share()` system share sheet\n170\t- Clear tap → `showDialog()` with `AlertDialog` → confirmation calls `clearAll()` and shows success snackbar\n171\t\n172\t---\n173\t\n174\t### Section 4: About\n175\t\n176\t**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n177\t\n178\t**Content:**\n179\tThree rows:\n180\t1. **App Version** — Static text row: \"Version\" label + version string from `pubspec.yaml` (e.g., \"1.0.0\"). Non-interactive.\n181\t2. **Privacy Policy** — `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → opens external URL (e.g., `https://example.com/privacy`).\n182\t3. **Terms of Service** — `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → opens external URL (e.g., `https://example.com/terms`).\n183\t\n184\t**Interactive Elements:**\n185\t- Privacy Policy tap → `url_launcher.launchUrl()` with privacy policy URL\n186\t- Terms of Service tap → `url_launcher.launchUrl()` with terms URL\n187\t\n188\t---\n189\t\n190\t## 7. Data\n191\t\n192\t### Entities\n193\t\n194\t| Entity | Provider | Key Fields |\n195\t|---|---|---|\n196\t| `UserPreferences` | `UserPreferencesProvider` | `name`, `notificationsEnabled`, `dueDate` |\n197\t| `PregnancyProfile` | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | `dueDate`, `currentWeek` |\n198\t\n199\t### Provider Scope\n200\t\n201\t- `UserPreferencesProvider` — manages name, notification preferences, due date (shared with PregnancyProfile)\n202\t- `PregnancyProfileProvider` — manages due date, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek\n203\t\n204\t### Export File Format\n205\t\n206\tJSON format containing:\n207\t```json\n208\t{\n209\t  \"exportDate\": \"ISO8601 timestamp\",\n210\t  \"user\": { \"name\": \"...\", \"dueDate\": \"...\" },\n211\t  \"pregnancyProfile\": { ... },\n212\t  \"moodEntries\": [ ... ],\n213\t  \"weightEntries\": [ ... ],\n214\t  \"symptomEntries\": [ ... ],\n215\t  \"cycleEntries\": [ ... ]\n216\t}\n217\t```\n218\t\n219\t---\n220\t\n221\t## 8. Motion\n222\t\n223\t### Screen Transition\n224\t- **Duration:** 300ms\n225\t- **Curve:** `Curves.easeInOut`\n226\t- **Type:** Slide + fade (standard push transition)\n227\t\n228\t### List Item Reveal\n229\t- **Stagger:** 50ms between each item (from top to bottom)\n230\t- **Type:** Fade + slight slide up\n231\t- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`\n232\t\n233\t### Toggle Switch\n234\t- **Duration:** 200ms\n235\t- **Type:** Thumb slide, track color transition\n236\t\n237\t### Card Tap Feedback\n238\t- **Duration:** 200ms\n239\t- **Type:** Scale to 98%, then return to 100%\n240\t- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`\n241\t\n242\t### Export Success\n243\t- **Duration:** 300ms\n244\t- **Type:** SnackBar fade in from bottom, auto-dismiss after 3s\n245\t\n246\t---\n247\t\n248\t## 9. Accessibility\n249\t\n250\t### Semantic Labels\n251\t- **Name field:** \"User name, [current name], double tap to edit\"\n252\t- **Due date:** \"Due date, [formatted date], double tap to change\"\n253\t- **Notification toggles:** \"[Category name], notifications [enabled/disabled], double tap to toggle\"\n254\t- **Export Data:** \"Export data, double tap to save and share your data\"\n255\t- **Clear All Data:** \"Clear all data, double tap to delete all app data. This action cannot be undone.\"\n256\t- **Privacy Policy:** \"Privacy policy, opens in browser\"\n257\t- **Terms of Service:** \"Terms of service, opens in browser\"\n258\t\n259\t### Touch Targets\n260\t- All interactive list items: minimum 56dp height\n261\t- All switches: 48dp minimum touch target\n262\t- All buttons: 48dp minimum height\n263\t\n264\t### Focus Order\n265\t1. Name field\n266\t2. Due date row\n267\t3. Daily Reminders toggle\n268\t4. Symptom Alerts toggle\n269\t5. Appointment Reminders toggle\n270\t6. Weekly Digest toggle\n271\t7. Export Data\n272\t8. Clear All Data\n273\t9. Privacy Policy\n274\t10. Terms of Service\n275\t\n276\t### Color Contrast\n277\t- Primary text (deepGraphite #1F2937) on morningMist (#FAFAFA): 12.8:1 ratio (AA compliant)\n278\t- Secondary text (stoneGrey #6B7280) on morningMist: 4.6:1 ratio (AA compliant)\n279\t- All text meets WCAG 2.1 AA contrast requirements\n280\t\n281\t---\n282\t\n283\t## 10. Anti-Patterns\n284\t\n285\t### Do NOT\n286\t- Use platform default colors — all colors from design token palette\n287\t- Show bottom navigation bar on this screen (hidden by navType: push)\n288\t- Use `AlertDialog` for anything other than destructive confirmation (clear data)\n289\t- Place critical actions (clear data) outside thumb zone (bottom two-thirds of screen)\n290\t- Use Inter or Roboto — Nunito only\n291\t- Use sharp corners — all cards 16dp radius, list items 12dp radius\n292\t- Use generic \"OK\" button labels — use action-specific labels (\"Delete\", \"Cancel\", \"Export\")\n293\t- Show FAB on this screen\n294\t- Use hardcoded strings — extract to localization keys"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3ddfff14-cec4-47ac-93d0-cd853b5c8ae4","uuid":"133ac7bd-e9f8-4c98-9dd0-0a7c8cb944a9","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:35:44.032Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/settings/SPEC.md","content":"# Settings Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n\n**Title:** Settings\n**Widget Name:** `SettingsScreen`\n**Screen ID:** `settings`\n\n---\n\n## 2. Purpose\n\nThe Settings screen allows users to manage their personal profile, configure notification preferences, export app data, and view legal/version information. It is a structured preference screen organized into four themed sections: Profile, Notifications, Data, and About.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Route\n\n**Route:** `/settings`\n**Navigation Type:** Push (from Profile tab or Settings icon in Home AppBar)\n**Swipe-back:** Enabled (dismisses to previous screen)\n\n---\n\n## 4. Design Tokens\n\n### Colors (Light Theme)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary actions, section headers, AppBar title |\n| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text (titles, names) |\n| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, descriptions |\n| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | List item borders, toggles off state |\n| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Clear data / destructive actions |\n| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states (export complete) |\n| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Card surfaces, bottom sheets |\n\n### Typography (Nunito)\n\n| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | Screen title |\n| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Section headers |\n| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | List item titles, field labels |\n| `bodySmall` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Descriptions, secondary text |\n| `caption` | 12sp | 400 | 16sp | Metadata, hints, version text |\n\n### Spacing (8pt Base)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n\n### Corner Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `card` | 16dp |\n| `listItem` | 12dp |\n\n### Motion\n\n| Motion | Duration | Curve |\n|---|---|---|\n| Screen push transition | 300ms | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n| List item stagger reveal | 50ms delay between items | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| Toggle switch thumb | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| Card tap feedback | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` (scale to 98%) |\n| Export success toast | 300ms fade in/out | `Curves.easeOut` |\n\n---\n\n## 5. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n\n```\nScaffold\n├── AppBar\n│   ├── Title: \"Settings\" (titleLarge, deepGraphite)\n│   ├── Back button (leading, 48dp touch target)\n│   └── No trailing icons\n├── BottomNavigationBar: Hidden\n├── FAB: None\n└── Body: ListView (sections separated by 24dp spacing)\n```\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n- Background: lavenderTint (#F5F3FF), transparent feel\n- Title: centered or left-aligned, SemiBold 20sp, deepGraphite\n- Back button: icon button with lavenderBloom color on tap\n- No actions/trailing widgets\n\n### Body Layout\n- Vertical `ListView` with `SliverAppBar` disabled (standard AppBar only)\n- Cards are wrapped in `Padding` with 16dp horizontal margin\n- 24dp vertical spacing between sections\n- 12dp vertical spacing between items within a section\n\n### Bottom Navigation Bar\n- Hidden on this screen (navType: push)\n\n---\n\n## 6. Sections\n\n### Section 1: Profile\n\n**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n\n**Content:**\n- **Name field** — `TextFormField` or tappable row that opens inline edit or bottom sheet. Label: \"Name\", value from `UserPreferences.name`.\n- **Due date row** — Tappable list tile showing due date. Label: \"Due Date\", value from `PregnancyProfile.dueDate` (also stored in `UserPreferences.dueDate`). Tapping triggers `showDatePicker` bottom sheet.\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `name` field\n- `PregnancyProfileProvider` — `dueDate` field\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Name tap → inline edit or bottom sheet with `TextEditingController`\n- Due date tap → `showDatePicker` bottom sheet, saves to both providers\n\n---\n\n### Section 2: Notifications\n\n**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n\n**Content:**\nA `Column` of `SwitchListTile` widgets, one per notification category:\n1. **Daily Reminders** — `UserPreferences.notifications.dailyReminders`\n2. **Symptom Alerts** — `UserPreferences.notifications.symptomAlerts`\n3. **Appointment Reminders** — `UserPreferences.notifications.appointmentReminders`\n4. **Weekly Digest** — `UserPreferences.notifications.weeklyDigest`\n\nEach switch:\n- Title: notification category name (titleMedium, deepGraphite)\n- Subtitle: brief description (bodySmall, stoneGrey)\n- Active track color: lavenderBloom; inactive track: mistyBorder\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `notificationsEnabled`, individual category flags\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Toggle switch → `UserPreferencesProvider.updateNotification(category, enabled)`\n- 200ms thumb slide animation\n\n---\n\n### Section 3: Data\n\n**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n\n**Content:**\nTwo action rows:\n1. **Export Data** — `InkWell` or `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → generates JSON/CSV file of all user data, triggers system share sheet.\n2. **Clear All Data** — `ListTile` with icon and label in softCoral color. Tap → `AlertDialog` confirmation (\"Are you sure? This action cannot be undone.\"), then calls `UserPreferencesProvider.clearAll()`.\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- `UserPreferencesProvider` — `clearAll()` method\n- Export uses all provider data (pregnancy profile, mood entries, weight entries, health log)\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Export tap → generate file → `Share.share()` system share sheet\n- Clear tap → `showDialog()` with `AlertDialog` → confirmation calls `clearAll()` and shows success snackbar\n\n---\n\n### Section 4: About\n\n**Card:** `Card` with morningMist background, 16dp corner radius, 16dp internal padding.\n\n**Content:**\nThree rows:\n1. **App Version** — Static text row: \"Version\" label + version string from `pubspec.yaml` (e.g., \"1.0.0\"). Non-interactive.\n2. **Privacy Policy** — `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → opens external URL (e.g., `https://example.com/privacy`).\n3. **Terms of Service** — `ListTile` with icon and label. Tap → opens external URL (e.g., `https://example.com/terms`).\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Privacy Policy tap → `url_launcher.launchUrl()` with privacy policy URL\n- Terms of Service tap → `url_launcher.launchUrl()` with terms URL\n\n---\n\n## 7. Data\n\n### Entities\n\n| Entity | Provider | Key Fields |\n|---|---|---|\n| `UserPreferences` | `UserPreferencesProvider` | `name`, `notificationsEnabled`, `dueDate` |\n| `PregnancyProfile` | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | `dueDate`, `currentWeek` |\n\n### Provider Scope\n\n- `UserPreferencesProvider` — manages name, notification preferences, due date (shared with PregnancyProfile)\n- `PregnancyProfileProvider` — manages due date, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek\n\n### Export File Format\n\nJSON format containing:\n```json\n{\n  \"exportDate\": \"ISO8601 timestamp\",\n  \"user\": { \"name\": \"...\", \"dueDate\": \"...\" },\n  \"pregnancyProfile\": { ... },\n  \"moodEntries\": [ ... ],\n  \"weightEntries\": [ ... ],\n  \"symptomEntries\": [ ... ],\n  \"cycleEntries\": [ ... ]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 8. Motion\n\n### Screen Transition\n- **Duration:** 300ms\n- **Curve:** `Curves.easeInOut`\n- **Type:** Slide + fade (standard push transition)\n\n### List Item Reveal\n- **Stagger:** 50ms between each item (from top to bottom)\n- **Type:** Fade + slight slide up\n- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`\n\n### Toggle Switch\n- **Duration:** 200ms\n- **Type:** Thumb slide, track color transition\n\n### Card Tap Feedback\n- **Duration:** 200ms\n- **Type:** Scale to 98%, then return to 100%\n- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`\n\n### Export Success\n- **Duration:** 300ms\n- **Type:** SnackBar fade in from bottom, auto-dismiss after 3s\n\n---\n\n## 9. Accessibility\n\n### Semantic Labels\n- **Name field:** \"User name, [current name], double tap to edit\"\n- **Due date:** \"Due date, [formatted date], double tap to change\"\n- **Notification toggles:** \"[Category name], notifications [enabled/disabled], double tap to toggle\"\n- **Export Data:** \"Export d